1.00	Melodifestivalen_1988	Melodifestivalen 1988	Melodifestivalen 1988 was the selection for the 28th song to represent Sweden at the Eurovision Song Contest. It was the 27th time that this system of picking a song had been used. 1100 songs were submitted to SVT for the competition. The final was broadcast on TV2 and was not broadcast on radio.	
